Feature: : LoginFunctionality
   As a user of the E-commerce application
  I want to be able to login into my account
  so that I can access personalised features make purchases

  Scenario: successful Login
    Given I am on the login page
    When  I check imagelogo is displayed
    And I check heading element is displayed
    And I check username element is dispalyed
    And I check password element is displayed
    And I check button is dispalyed








  Scenario: Successful Login
    Given I am on the login page
    When I enter valid username and password
    And I click on the login button
    Then I should be redirected to the home page